      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation software (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) is under configuration control with documented version history; FDA-internal solver verified against published benchmarks.",
      "rationale": "All three modeling teams (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under documented software QA procedures. Version-controlled input decks and solver executables were archived prior to analysis. Achieved level meets required level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
